response.overview: After a long day of working long and hard at the sriracha t shirt factory, our protagonist Gunt takes a leisurely stroll past the flickering golden blades of grass and knee high tulip flowers in his own backyard to relax and have a elf bar and la Croix picnic by himself. However, when a friendly stranger approaches him, he's left with a choice that could alter the rest of his life
response.title: Gunts Picnic
